### Listar vagas
GET http://localhost:4500/postsvagas

### Listar vagas por usuario
GET http://localhost:4500/postsvagas/usuario/3

### Criar vaga com imagem
POST http://localhost:4500/postsvagas
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=MyBoundary

--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="arquivo"; filename="vaga.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./foto.jpg
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="user_id"

3
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="titulo"

Vaga para designer grafico
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="vaga"

Designer grafico pleno
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="descricao_vaga"

Descricao completa da vaga e requisitos principais.
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="datapost_vaga"

2026-04-14
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tipovaga_post"

presencial
--MyBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="localizacao_vaga"

Sao Paulo, SP
--MyBoundary--
